:R-HSA-9025106  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0042759 ;
        rdfs:comment        "The biosynthesis of specialised proresolving mediators (SPMs) derived from the ω-6 isomer of DPA, DPAn-6 (cis-4,7,10,13,16-docosapentaenoic acid) is described here (Dangi et al. 2010). The products of the ω-6 isomer were characterised by analogy in structure and action to docosahexaenoic acid (DHA)-derived and eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA)-derived resolvins (Serhan et al. 2002, Bannenberg & Serhan 2010)." ;
        rdfs:label          "Biosynthesis of DPAn-6 SPMs" ;
        dc:contributor      "GOC:reactome_curators" , "Edited: Jassal, Bijay, 2017-10-12" , "Authored: Jassal, Bijay, 2017-10-12" , "Reviewed: Hansen, Trond Vidar, 2018-02-21" ;
        dc:date             "2026-06-29" ;
